Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,~Dialogue~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.79,0:00:15.11,Default,Armed Disciplinary Officer,0,0,0,,西園寺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.11,0:00:18.36,Default,Armed Disciplinary Officer,0,0,0,,挾持女生作人質  也太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:22.91,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,卑鄙？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:25.88,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,這對我來說可是稱讚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:29.44,Default,Saionji,1200,0,0,,積極  健康  向上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:32.38,Default,Saionji,1200,0,0,,那種事情機器人也能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:35.99,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,我要卑鄙  下流  無情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:38.19,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,為了目的不擇手段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:43.76,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,因為我是遵從黑暗武士道的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:52.23,Default,Wholesome Member A,0,0,0,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:54.58,Default,Wholesome Member A,0,0,0,,像是 20 世紀的動畫一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:58.44,Default,Wholesome Member B,0,0,0,,他真的是主人公嗎？ 不是反派？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:01:01.01,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,他就是主人公！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:03.76,Default,Wholesome Member A,0,0,0,,田  田口先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:09.75,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,這個主人公他偷拐搶騙  恣意妄為
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:15.25,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,更可怕的是  他從來不會因此受到報應
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:19.51,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,這是在正當化有違道德的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:22.49,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,比色情血腥更加危險
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.57,0:01:26.27,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,這個作品…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:30.84,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,現在在孩子中非常有影響力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.30,0:01:37.40,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,讓我們來改變現狀吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.06,0:01:43.13,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,讓這邪典動畫徹底消失！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:45.56,Default,Wholesome Members,0,0,0,,徹底消失！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:23.72,Default,Navi,0,0,0,,距目的地還剩 20 分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:27.82,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,因為我的父母思想非常守舊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:31.64,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,所以我未曾能夠盡情享受虛擬娛樂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:37.02,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,我不想讓自己孩子也經歷同樣的體驗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:43.24,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,價值觀是隨時代變化的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:46.01,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,而不應該是父母硬加給孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:51.00,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,我希望孩子能夠隨好奇心驅使  去探索嘗試各種事物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:55.68,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,我真是懷著這樣的想法把他們養大的  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:58.10,Default,Taguchi's Wife,0,0,0,,該吃飯囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.71,Default,Taguchi Son,0,0,0,,無論男女老少  擋我者死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.76,Default,Taguchi Daughter,0,0,0,,擋我者死！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:08.04,Default,Taguchi Wife,0,0,0,,喂  不要這麼說話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:08.83,Default,Taguchi Wife,0,0,0,,該吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:11.55,Default,Taguchi Son,0,0,0,,不想被捕食就快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:13.06,Default,Taguchi Daughter,0,0,0,,吃吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:18.17,Default,Taguchi Son,900,0,0,,黑暗  黑暗  黑暗  黑暗  黑暗武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:19.82,Default,Taguchi Daughter,0,800,0,,黑暗武士道  西園寺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:26.45,Top - s,Kids,0,0,0,,黑暗  黑暗  黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:24.93,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,感覺  煩死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:30.91,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,『黑暗武士道』那種邪典動畫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:34.34,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,絕不能放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:38.17,Default,Wholesome Member B,0,0,0,,既然作品是如此  創作者大概也不是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:41.17,Default,Wholesome Member B,0,0,0,,對本站發出的電話採訪請求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:45.68,Default,Wholesome Member B,0,0,0,,『黑暗武士道』的導演小山田茄子如此回應道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:48.80,Default,Wholesome Member B,0,0,0,,「有意見就當面跟我說」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:51.18,Default,Wholesome Member B,0,0,0,,「但要做好以死相博的準備」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:55.44,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,嗯  所以怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:58.65,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,你們想要怎麼處理我的動畫？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:01.89,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,我說啊  小山田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:04.94,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,你做的是給小孩子看的動畫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:07.92,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,希望你能夠保守最基本的倫理底線
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:10.61,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,什麼倫理底線？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:13.16,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,那是你們畫的線嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:16.87,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,你當然是有創作自由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:18.39,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,但是我們也有權發聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:20.54,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,怎  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:21.87,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,撒尿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:34.12,Default,Wholesome Member B,0,0,0,,我還以為動畫是要很多人才能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.78,Default,Wholesome Member B,0,0,0,,沒想到他一個人就做了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:38.23,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,這就是問題所在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:41.57,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,和過去不同  現在光靠一個人就能隨意創作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:46.20,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,所以審查才會失效  導致各種邪典的出現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:50.49,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,畫面的魅力很強  對於兒童來說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:54.70,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:01.93,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,小  小山田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:07.22,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,是貧血
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:10.97,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你的生活習慣太不健康了  小山田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:13.76,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,又受你照顧了  醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:14.98,Default,Wholesome Member B,0,0,0,,又？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:19.34,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,到這裡來就能吃到營養代餐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:22.04,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我們的只是醫療用的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:25.44,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,雖然難吃  但比外面賣的便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:30.32,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,不惜搞壞身體  你究竟在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:33.83,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,為什麼不做點更有意義的作品呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:39.01,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,我只是在做想做的作品而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:40.83,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,你是不會理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:42.09,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:47.56,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,如果社會繼續迎合你們這樣的好好青年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:49.85,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,壞事會不斷增加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:53.39,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,你在胡說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:56.25,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,這個國家的犯罪率每年都在降低  正…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:57.84,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:02.48,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,我是說會有更多的事會被認定為「惡」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.93,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,開車就是一個例子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:08.63,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,現在自己開車的人  都會被罵做是殺人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:13.44,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,總有一天  只要身為人類就會稱為惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.29,Default,Wholesome B,0,0,0,,他在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.36,Default,Wholesome B,0,0,0,,就好像他根本沒做壞事一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:26.75,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:29.64,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,他要是不創作邪惡的題材
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:32.73,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,就沒辦法在這個 AI 社會表現自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:38.63,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,因為那種肯定邪惡的故事  是 AI 無法想像出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.63,0:07:39.64,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,在倫理上來講
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:41.47,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,他們是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:46.00,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,嗯  「兒童健康什麼什麼」的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:49.74,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,話說醫生  我現在是病人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:52.32,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,給我營養代餐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:01.59,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,天真  太傻白甜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:04.70,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,比糖尿病大叔的尿還要甜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:08.92,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,就憑這種攻擊也想要阻止我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:18.01,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,有趣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:20.81,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,你的玩具挺不錯的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:23.77,Default,Beautiful Student Council President,0,0,0,,武裝風紀委員長  這太過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.83,Default,Sainoji,0,0,0,,好了  來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:34.66,Default,Sainoji,0,0,0,,我會拼上性命和你決鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:51.30,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,等等  小山田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:53.86,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,今天可不會讓你跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:55.71,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,我沒跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:58.05,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,須堂醫生叫我過去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:00.04,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,我只是去做定期體檢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:03.31,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,我可是收集到了這麼多簽名哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:06.08,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,你給我看也沒用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:08.42,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,去拿給政府什麼的看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:16.41,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,看到這麼一疊文件  你就不會良心不安嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.55,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,小山田先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:20.43,Default,Punk A,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:26.92,Default,Punk A,0,0,0,,你小子  撞了人就這麼無視了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:29.42,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:33.42,Default,Punk A,0,0,0,,賠錢啊  雜種
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.42,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,你  你們說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:37.69,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,是想要恐嚇大人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:38.91,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,在這種大街上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:40.95,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,你想要毀掉自己的人生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:42.72,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,快住手  不要刺激他們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:44.39,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,你看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:48.40,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,就是因為你正面描繪不良行為  這種人才會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:00.38,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:05.41,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,你們贏了  就算了吧  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:08.73,Default,Punk A,0,0,0,,大叔你是他的同伴嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.22,Default,Punk A,0,0,0,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:14.67,Default,Punk A,0,0,0,,你也給我賠錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:22.47,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,交  交叉迎擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:29.15,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,抱歉  不由得就出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:38.74,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,不要讓我濫用我賴以吃飯的工具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:45.30,Default,Punk B,0,0,0,,喂  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:47.36,Default,Punk A,0,0,0,,我要宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:48.96,Default,Punk B,0,0,0,,喂… 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:51.40,Default,Punk A,0,0,0,,他也是仿生人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:53.46,Default,Punk A,0,0,0,,死是不會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:55.75,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,小  小山田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:02.92,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:05.66,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,我會拼上性命和你決鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:16.27,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,治療結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.53,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,小山田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:20.53,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:26.61,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,我聽護士說你不打算報警  你是認真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:29.71,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,只是幾個見血就嚇跑了的小人物罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:34.17,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,你為什麼保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.43,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,大反派也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:40.42,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,但我也喜歡描繪今天這樣的小惡黨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:43.52,Default,Taguchi,0,0,0,,小惡黨!? 他可是割傷了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:45.68,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,你會這麼想也沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:49.00,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,如果我們就像這樣  不斷縮小邪惡的陣地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:50.68,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,等到完全消失的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:53.69,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,剩下的就不能再稱之為人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:57.24,Default,Oyamada,0,0,0,,而是  曾是人類的某種事物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:02.70,Default,Taguchi Son,0,0,0,,西園寺是個壞蛋  但有時也是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.26,Default,Taguchi Son,0,0,0,,我就是喜歡這種
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:11.71,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,好弱  好弱雞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:15.21,Default,Beautiful Student Council President,0,0,0,,明  明明把我作為肉盾的話  你就能輕鬆取勝的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:17.23,Default,Beautiful Student Council President,0,0,0,,西園寺同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:18.19,Default,Beautiful Student Council President,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:21.09,Default,Beautiful Student Council President,0,0,0,,其實是個好人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:26.70,Default,Saionji,0,0,0,,我可是遵從黑暗武士道的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:36.11,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,教書育人是人類非常重要的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:38.98,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,就算產業 AI 有多發達
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:43.24,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,也應當由人類型智慧來主導現場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:48.74,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,小學是兒童樹立自我的重要時期
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:51.32,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,產業 AI 的算法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:55.75,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,可能會導致感情細膩的兒童偏離人性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:13:01.84,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,屬於人類的  源於人類的  為人類服務的教育
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:05.13,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,這是本校的教育政策
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:09.94,Default,Friend,0,0,0,,所以  你真的要去那裡工作嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:11.85,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,畢竟拿到內定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:13.73,Default,Friend,0,0,0,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:16.49,Default,Friend,0,0,0,,那裡在業界的風評很差
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:21.26,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,我聽說那裡因為歧視仿生人上過新聞什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:23.27,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,但那是很久之前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:25.22,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,現在負責管理的人已經換了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:27.77,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,現在他們非常重視透明度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:32.02,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,還會將教室即時直播給家長們什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:34.28,Default,Friend,0,0,0,,這真的沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.75,Default,Friend,0,0,0,,隱私方面什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:37.45,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,這沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:40.75,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,因為不是自家的孩子都會打上馬賽克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:44.97,Default,Friend,0,0,0,,打馬賽克的時是使用的 AI 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:47.97,Default,Friend,0,0,0,,這方針有點不太對勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:54.07,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,總之似乎就是不使用 AI 參與授課就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:57.18,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,教室裡也不設機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:02.11,Default,Friend,0,0,0,,在這個時代還這麼搞  我真是搞不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:04.11,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:07.02,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,實話說我也這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:10.91,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,但其他的學校全都應聘失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:17.16,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,雖說也可以給你數字版的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:20.21,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,但總之你好好看一遍這本手冊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:23.72,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,學校內的情況  家長全都能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.22,0:14:27.72,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,大家都是為了這份安心  才選擇的本校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:32.21,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,所以要注意對待學生的方法  不要引來投訴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:33.56,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:36.79,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,回答不可以這麼隨便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:38.30,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,是  是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:43.98,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,在這個國家的小學和國中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:46.91,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,很多都在教室裡設置得有機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:49.08,Default,Student A,0,0,0,,喂  能教我這道題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:50.62,Default,Support Robot,0,0,0,,好的  沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:53.60,Default,Support Robot,0,0,0,,四則運算呢  要先…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:53.99,Default,Student B,1200,0,0,,你真敢啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:55.38,Default,Student C,0,0,0,,是你的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:57.11,Default,Support Robot,0,0,0,,不可以打架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.33,Default,Support Robot,0,0,0,,不可以打架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:03.34,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,機器人在各種場合都非常有用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:09.31,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,讓 AI 做教育顧問也是很常見的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:14.18,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,但是  我也不能為了他一個人降低課程的節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:20.08,Default,Educational Advisor AI,0,0,0,,自尊心和理解度是成正相關的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:22.63,Default,Educational Advisor AI,0,0,0,,不如敞開胸懷好好談談
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:24.96,Default,Educational Advisor AI,0,0,0,,不再以教師和學生的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:29.26,Default,Educational Advisor AI,0,0,0,,而是以朋友的身份重新建立關係怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:33.45,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,嗯  好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:38.32,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,有很多教師照本宣科地按照 AI 的指示來教育學生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:43.71,Default,Guardian,0,0,0,,我想要他成為一個有人性的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.46,Default,Guardian,0,0,0,,他擁有著世界獨一無二的寶貴個性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:49.94,Default,Guardian,0,0,0,,這是沒辦法託付給量產型的產業 AI 的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:57.22,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:16:01.98,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,如果說家長相信人類和仿生人教師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:04.34,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,事實也並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:10.44,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,今天不上課  所以沒有直播  放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:12.86,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,好  好…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:13.73,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,你的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:15.37,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,對  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:18.17,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,那就開始模擬課程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:19.05,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:24.41,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,各位同學  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:25.42,Default,Manager,0,0,0,,太早了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:30.02,Default,Manager,0,0,0,,班會還有 30 秒才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:31.60,Default,Manager,0,0,0,,要是之後還有學生進來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:34.57,Default,Manager,0,0,0,,就會覺得自己遲到了  從而感到一種疏遠感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:39.52,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,我只是打了個招呼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:42.23,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,班會還沒有開始啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:44.11,Default,Manager,0,0,0,,那也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:45.61,Default,Manager,0,0,0,,以前有過投訴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:46.60,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:50.75,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,你要在預訂時間的前後三秒內進入教室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:54.07,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,給你的手冊上也寫得清清楚楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:57.53,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,在明天前把它給記牢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.49,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,你的回答呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.19,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:07.51,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,總之就是規矩繁多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:09.92,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,全是不准做這  不准做那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:16.43,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,像是必須用姓加「同學」來稱呼孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:20.60,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,還要格外注意不能差別對待學生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:24.33,Default,Friend,0,0,0,,父母監視得嚴嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:27.30,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,看得挺嚴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:32.46,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,我這就已經收到 3 次投訴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:35.70,Default,Friend,0,0,0,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:45.83,Default,School Announcement,0,0,0,,二年級給大家帶來的「幸福快樂舞蹈」到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:50.39,Default,School Announcement,0,0,0,,接下來是三年級給大家帶來的虛擬疊羅漢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:52.96,Default,School Announcement,0,0,0,,「大大大大金字塔」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:59.12,Default,School Announcement,0,0,0,,您看  孩子們開始精神同步了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:02.89,Default,School Announcement,0,0,0,,請看您植入物的 AR 畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:08.98,Default,School Announcement,0,0,0,,孩子們的分身浮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:15.49,Default,School Announcement,0,0,0,,現在  同學們的心念合一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:22.55,Default,School Announcement,0,0,0,,組成了大大的金字塔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:27.31,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,虛擬疊羅漢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:29.10,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,也算是運動嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:33.00,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,這是我校特有的活動  廣受家長們的好評
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:36.51,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,自然  這麼做不會受傷  而且更重要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:40.10,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,在家長自己的 AR 世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:43.41,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,都看到的是自己孩子在頂端
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:46.64,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,看到自己的孩子是最受矚目的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.65,Default,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,所以家長們都非常滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:55.81,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,建立在這種利害關係上  處處受限的「公平」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:57.92,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:01.86,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,這份公平真的有人性嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:05.75,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,這所學校  真的有人性嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:12.14,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,在監視中  教師們都害怕與學生交流
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:14.94,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,只會進行機械化的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:18.18,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,不對問題兒童生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:20.18,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,也不去陪伴幫助他們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:23.29,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,只是默默地將其勸退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:30.66,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,我做教師不是為了來做這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:33.94,Default,Onishi,0,0,0,,喂  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:36.69,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,怎  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:39.31,Default,Onishi,0,0,0,,你看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:45.45,Default,Onishi,0,0,0,,我得了特等獎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:47.79,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,真是太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:52.54,Default,Onishi,0,0,0,,都是因為老師您叫我投稿  才會有今天！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:54.29,Default,Onishi,0,0,0,,謝謝你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.81,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,我聽教導主任說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:06.60,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,說是你請書法社的學生喝了飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:09.79,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,因為大西同學得了特等獎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:13.60,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,我才約好給他一點獎勵…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:15.59,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,天氣也很熱…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:20.36,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,你還沒理解我們的政策啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:22.81,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,這是個很嚴重的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:30.70,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,有什麼大不了的嘛  不就一杯飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:32.60,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,這才是人性化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:48.09,Default,Coworker,0,0,0,,不要假扮人類  給別人添麻煩啊  白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:53.36,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,教師不是機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:56.38,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,是擁有著缺點和偏見的人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.72,0:21:03.61,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,我本想著… 哪怕為了學生  也要堅持教完一年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:07.77,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,但是… 他們對待我的態度越來越差
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:14.37,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我可以給你開一些藥物治療
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:18.13,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,但改變環境是最好的良藥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:27.28,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,從學校辭職差不多一年後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:31.68,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,我開始在一家特殊教育機構幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:33.51,Default,Perm,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:34.58,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:37.06,Default,Toshiki,0,0,0,,不公平  怎麼只給洋同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:41.65,Default,Perm,0,0,0,,等俊樹同學你下次考出好成績  我就給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:44.39,Default,Free School Teacher,0,0,0,,他雖是看護機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.39,0:21:48.34,Default,Free School Teacher,0,0,0,,但他的 AI 是在學校裡訓練的  所以很擅長看顧兒童
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:54.66,Default,Free School Teacher,0,0,0,,無法融入學校的兒童
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.66,0:21:57.44,Default,Free School Teacher,0,0,0,,害怕成年人的兒童
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:21:59.68,Default,Free School Teacher,0,0,0,,各式各樣的兒童都會來我們這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:04.62,Default,Free School Teacher,0,0,0,,你的經驗一定也能在這裡派上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.71,0:22:11.22,Default,Shinohara,0,0,0,,不知道家長們對帕瑪同學是什麼看法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:14.57,Default,Free School Teacher,0,0,0,,大家都說他是專業看護員  所以值得信賴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:18.56,Default,Free School Teacher,0,0,0,,不過在你聽來  可能是十分諷刺
